==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Theobromic
<hw>The`o*bro"mic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of, pertaining to, or designating, an acid extracted from cacao
butter (from the <xex>Theobroma Cacao</xex>), peanut oil (from
<xex>Arachis hypogaea</xex>), etc., as a white waxy crystalline
substance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Theobromine</ent>⟦br⟧
